name: Corset Piercing
description:
A model for corset piercings. I wasn't sure how it'd turn out considering the small data set but I am very impressed.

Quirks:
It will try to lift clothes so I would suggest 'clothes lift' in the negatives. There were only two images with lifted clothes, but with the size of the data set I guess that was a big deal.
On rare occasions it will put the zigzag-ing lace on the clothes like an actual corset ignoring the piercing.
Corset should go in the negatives to avoid getting them occasionally.
The piercing counts as clothes so when trying to prompt nudity with the piercing do '(nude:0.8)' in order to not remove it.

Things to try:
Try placing the piercing where you want it. It will do 'corset piercing on': back, thigh, stomach, or arm.
Try changing the color. It does red or black very easily but it can also handle similar colors such as pink or dark blue.
Try it on realistic models. From some testing it works well!
Try it without prompting for the piercing as it makes cool outfits.
Try it with my goth LoRA. The last image was made with both.

As usual:
Trained on Anything v3
Demos are Anything v4.5 with LoRA weight 0.8
Note the last image is using my Goth LoRA as well in case that was missed earlier
NSFW images towards the end of the demos

If you get any cool gens share them in the comments!
